<MoneyPageLayout
  title="ITIN Business Loans: Fund Your Business Without an SSN (2026)"
  h1="ITIN Business Loans"
  description="How to finance a business with an ITIN. Term loans, lines of credit, microloans, CDFIs, and how to build business credit as an immigrant entrepreneur."
  path="/itin-business-loans"
  eyebrow="Business financing"
  lede="Building a business in the U.S. with an ITIN? You have more financing paths than most people realize. Here's how to fund and grow your company."
